ELK/Logstash收集多种Filebeat数据.html.body:
ELK - Logstash收集多种Filebeat数据，如何区分不同来源
比如Filebeat。
Logstash Filer Grok
Logstash配置可以使用if [fields][type]来区分来源。
test.conf
input {
  beats {
    port => 5044
  }
}

filter {
  if [fields][type] == "test" {
    grok {
      match => { "message" => "%{DATESTAMP:logTime}%-%{GREEDYDATA:message}" }
      overwrite => [ "message" ]
    }
  }
}

output {
  if [fields][type] == "test" {
    stdout { codec => rubydebug }
  }
  if "_grokparsefailure" in [tags] {
    file { "path" => "/tmp/grok_failures.log" }
  }
}

Filebeat
Filebeat配置相应的加上fields.type定义。
vi /etc/filebeat/filebeat.yml
- type: log

  # Change to true to enable this input configuration.
  enabled: true

  # Paths that should be crawled and fetched. Glob based paths.
  paths:
    - /var/log/*.log
  fields:
    type: test

#output.elasticsearch:
  # Array of hosts to connect to.
  #hosts: ["localhost:9200"]

output.logstash:
